  <entry>
    <id>https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/releases/tag/v2.11.0</id>
    <title>New release for Pachli: Pachli 2.11.0</title>
    <updated>2025-03-31T06:11:48-04:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>pachli/pachli-android</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h3&gt;New features and other improvements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Replace Atkinson Hyperlegible with "Next" variant (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1425"&gt;1425&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support translation throughout the app (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1414"&gt;1414&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make new content filters default to active in all contexts (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1389"&gt;1389&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement Markdown rendering, controlled by a lab preference (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1353"&gt;1353&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Significant bug fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stop the report UI from sometimes hanging, honour Markdown setting (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1419"&gt;1419&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Always set an accessible description on the "Toot" button (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1415"&gt;1415&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don't crash when determining upload MIME type (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1402"&gt;1402&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don't crash if download error happens when sharing media (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1401"&gt;1401&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don't crash when processing severed relationship notifications (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1400"&gt;1400&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prevent crash on long press if span is not attached (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1394"&gt;1394&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reduce risk of ANR, only call ExoPlayer release() when the command is available (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1393"&gt;1393&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create filters with the correct content-type (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1390"&gt;1390&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve display of lists of content filters (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1388"&gt;1388&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Filter correctly in threads and private messages (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1387"&gt;1387&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support editing captions of uploaded images (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1382"&gt;1382&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Allow Report notifications with a null &lt;code&gt;forwarded&lt;/code&gt; property (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1372"&gt;1372&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Correctly parse &lt;code&gt;action_taken&lt;/code&gt; and similar in report notifications (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1371"&gt;1371&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show join date in grammatically correct form (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1367"&gt;1367&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Translations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Finnish translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=kalle.kniivila@gmail.com"&gt;Kalle Kniivilä&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Indonesian translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=182783629+doctorreditshere@users.noreply.github.com"&gt;Doctorredits_here&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Irish translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=aindriu80@gmail.com"&gt;Aindriú Mac Giolla Eoin&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Latvian translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=Edgars+Weblate@gaitenis.id.lv"&gt;Edgars Andersons&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Norwegian Nynorsk translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=sunniva@users.noreply.hosted.weblate.org"&gt;sunniva&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Polish translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=dakilla@gmail.com"&gt;Łukasz Horodecki&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Slovak translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=russssty@users.noreply.hosted.weblate.org"&gt;Russssty&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Spanish translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=jumase@disroot.org"&gt;Juan M Sevilla&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/releases/tag/v2.11.0" rel="alternate"/>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <id>https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/releases/tag/v2.12.0</id>
    <title>New release for Pachli: Pachli 2.12.0</title>
    <updated>2025-04-30T08:44:15-04:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>pachli/pachli-android</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h3&gt;New features and other improvements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update colour scheme, adjusts contrast (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1452"&gt;1452&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Move tab-tap behaviour preference out of "Lab experiments" (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1477"&gt;1477&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve the display of admin notifications (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1475"&gt;1475&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enable client-side encrypted cloud backups (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1457"&gt;1457&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lab support for exporting/importing preferences (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1451"&gt;1451&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show hashtag usage and account stats in search results (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1442"&gt;1442&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show hashtag statistics in the Followed Tags screen (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1433"&gt;1433&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sort followed hashtags by hashtag name (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1432"&gt;1432&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Significant bug fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Show translated posts / media descriptions when viewing threads (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1504"&gt;1504&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don't error on nullable &lt;code&gt;Report.actionTakenAt&lt;/code&gt; property (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1474"&gt;1474&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set initial reading position for non-cached timelines to the top (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1468"&gt;1468&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Allow filtering of mentions and severed relationships on older devices (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1454"&gt;1454&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prevent crash, correctly pass report data to notifications (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1449"&gt;1449&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=im@austinhuang.me"&gt;Austin Huang&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Allow clicks anywhere on FollowedTag view (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1445"&gt;1445&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prevent "Record not found" when opening as a different account (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1431"&gt;1431&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Translations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Finnish translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=kalle.kniivila@gmail.com"&gt;Kalle Kniivilä&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Irish translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=aindriu80@gmail.com"&gt;Aindriú Mac Giolla Eoin&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Latvian translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=Edgars+Weblate@gaitenis.id.lv"&gt;Edgars Andersons&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Latvian translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=coool@mail.lv"&gt;ℂ𝕠𝕠𝕠𝕝 (𝕘𝕚𝕥𝕙𝕦𝕓.𝕔𝕠𝕞/ℂ𝕠𝕠𝕠𝕝)&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Polish translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=dakilla@gmail.com"&gt;Łukasz Horodecki&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Slovak translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=russssty@users.noreply.hosted.weblate.org"&gt;Russssty&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update Spanish translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=jumase@disroot.org"&gt;Juan M Sevilla&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
