  <entry>
    <id>https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/releases/tag/v2.13.0</id>
    <title>New release for Pachli: Pachli 2.13.0</title>
    <updated>2025-05-28T10:38:33-04:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>pachli/pachli-android</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h3&gt;New features and other improvements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Parse Instants from servers that don't include the timezone (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1544"&gt;1544&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Replace Local timeline with Trending in default tabs (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1543"&gt;1543&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make media descriptions more important when composing (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1516"&gt;1516&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Significant bug fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use alpha instead of colour for disabled items when composing (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1542"&gt;1542&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve colours when compose buttons are enabled (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1541"&gt;1541&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Display poll previews correctly (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1540"&gt;1540&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don't crash if ComposeActivity is destroyed while taking a picture (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1537"&gt;1537&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don't leak MainActivity in DrawerImageLoader (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1536"&gt;1536&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure transition/animation listener is always removed (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1530"&gt;1530&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create/pass MainActivity payload through IntentRouterActivity (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1532"&gt;1532&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Start-align "Vote" button's position (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1524"&gt;1524&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
