    <author>
      <name>pachli/pachli-android</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h3&gt;New features and other improvements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restore the user's reading position in lists (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1548"&gt;1548&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Speed up account switching if the user has no account filters (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1564"&gt;1564&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide an "Account Management" UI (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1557"&gt;1557&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Significant bug fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Delete cached notifications when deleting server notifications (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1585"&gt;1585&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don't crash when receiving severed relationship notifications (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1572"&gt;1572&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don't crash when cancelling images during activity cancellation (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1562"&gt;1562&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prevent IndexOutOfBoundsException on text long press (#&lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/pull/1561"&gt;1561&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://github.com/pachli/pachli-android/commits?author=nik@ngo.org.uk"&gt;Nik Clayton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
